facts_and_links: {'Trivia': ['Michael Schumacher, the Rain Master/King, aka the Red Dragon. Seven times Formula One (F1) World Champion, of which five of them were in a row with Scuderia Ferrari (2000-2004). Michael dedicated his first F1 championship title in 1994 to the late Ayrton Senna. Michael has 91 Formula 1 race wins to his name.
